text: The Sorani Koli (also spelled as Saurani Koli and Sourani Koli) is a clan (Gotra) of the Koli caste found in the Indian state of Gujarat and the Union Territory of Daman and Diu and nearby areas. == See more == *Koli rebellion *Koli clans and titles *Koli clans of Gujarat *Koli dance *Koli pirates == References == Category:Koli clans
